# Keymap


## General

~~~

alt key                         Menu option                                                     Alt
alt (in dialog)                 Shows letter select button

~~~

## Editing

~~~

fn / alt [left / right]         Next / Previous Word                                            Alt [left / right]    
fn / alt agift [left / right]   Select Next / Previous Word                                     Alt [left / right]    
fn / alt [up / down]            Extend / Shrink selection                                       Alt [up / down]

ctrl shift j                    Smart join

ctrl space                      Code completion
ctrl shift space                Smart code completion
alt space                       Quick definition                                                Alt space
cmd p                           Parameter info                                                  Alt p
cmd shift return                Complete statement                                              Alt shift return

alt / cmd return                Intention actions & quick fixes                                 Alt return
F2                              Next highlighted error
cmd F1                          Show error / warning description at carat                       Alt F1
cmd F1                          Show inpection description                                      Alt F1
F1                              Quick documentation lookup, 
                                repeat opens doc window, repeat removes

cmd n                           Generate code                                                   Alt n
cmd shift l                     Reformat code                                                   Alt shift l
cmd fn o                        Optimize imports                                                Alt ctrl o

ctrl tab                        Switcher
cmd e                           Recent files & windows                                          Alt e                       

~~~

## Navigation

~~~
F4                              Jump to source

~~~

## Compile & Run

~~~
ctrl shift r                    Run..
                                Tests - creates a run configuration
                                Services - runs a spring app, http script etc
                                HTTP Requests - runs a request

ctrl shift r                    Rerun (services)

cmd F2                          Stop (spring app)

ctrl alt cmd r                  Run configurations

~~~

## VCS

~~~
cmd k                           commit                                  Alt k
cmd shift k                     commit & push                           Alt shift k

~~~




========================================================================================================================


~~~




alt cmd [left / right]          Navigate forwards / backwards

cmd shift arrow                 Resize window


cmd j                           Insert live template
alt cmd j                       Surround with live template

ctrl v                          VCS popup
~~~

---

### Remapped keys

~~~
ctrl alt [left / right]         Move to next / previous word in different CamelHumps mode
                                (urrently full words instead of camel humps (the default)

shift ctrl return               Insert line above

fn ctrl [up / down]             Next / previous method         

alt m                           Context menu

fn ctrl alt [left / right]      Next / previous splitter
alt cmd [left / right]          Next / previous tab

fn ctrl right                   Fully expand tree node

ctrl alt cmd r                  Select configuration

ctrl esc                        Jump to last tool window

cmd s                           Build Project (replaces save all)

ctrl +                          Increase font size
ctrl -                          Decrease font size
ctrl =                          Reset font size
~~~
 
### Abbreviations

~~~
or      Open recent
cp      Close project
mp      Manage projects
np      New Project
~~~
